ReplyText: We must get close to help!
SSRewardText:
The pirates flee when they see you approaching; it seems they’ve already gotten what they wanted. 

As you get closer, you notice that the nautical machine is damaged, with water leaking inside, but you might have time to inspect it if you’re quick. You decide to board the submarine and explore it, but there’s no trace of the crew. 

The machine is very narrow, and you unintentionally activate something, causing it to dive and sail to an unknown undersea facility on autopilot, with you inside.
